channel.title: RuneScape Caches
channel.description:
Ive got a question, whens the last time you loaded/logged into runescape? Im on a cache hunt and need a specific version.
Im looking for a cache somewhere between 2005-2008, this will be used to take the client out of, and then create a private server that will connect to it. It will help the community, because once jagex updates runescape and you load the game, your old cache will overwrite... So to find out just PLEASE do this for me guys, appriciate it...
Start -> My computer -> (c:) -> WINDOWS -> .jagex_cache_32
Right click it and press properties, where it says "Created: Etc" If it is anywhere from 2005-2008 please .zip it and upload it here through a site like uppit, megaupload, etc.
Well thanks again guys, please take your time to do this as it means ALOT for me and the members of the community who need this.
